 epilogue level offered only to the ones who can complete the majority of the tests, or get high enough scores in certain levels and receive the invitation earlier this way.<br><br>Also each level unlocks new character customization options: <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887720/extras/7e7df015329eadbd9deee05a2b025072.poster.avif?t=1714053178\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887720/extras/7e7df015329eadbd9deee05a2b025072.webm?t=1714053178\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887720/extras/7e7df015329eadbd9deee05a2b025072.mp4?t=1714053178\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Many levels also give a deeper glimpse into the strange world this takes place on: <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887720/extras/06e284669d1bbcbf3a5a4b3bb60627d7.avif?t=1714053178\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br>And why is the world cube shaped anyway? <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887720/extras/d6fd6d5be0c12e4ef3c9aeb6cc46e74c.poster.avif?t=1714053178\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887720/extras/d6fd6d5be0c12e4ef3c9aeb6cc46e74c.webm?t=1714053178\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887720/extras/d6fd6d5be0c12e4ef3c9aeb6cc46e74c.mp4?t=1714053178\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
